---
name: Custom Checkboxes and Radio Buttons
description: These are available with special code that needs to be precicely used.
order: 1
notes: |
    - use `mzp-c-input-choice` for both checkboxes and radio buttons
    - the input must be before the label in source order
    - nothing else can go inside the parent div
---


<div class="mzp-c-input-choice">
  <input type="radio" name="radio-c1" id="radio-c1">
  <label for="radio-c1">Radio button</label>
</div>

<div class="mzp-c-input-choice">
  <input type="checkbox" name="checkboxes" id="checkbox-c1">
  <label for="checkbox-c1">Checkbox</label>
</div>

<p>Fieldset necissary for user feedback states:</p>
<fieldset class="mzp-c-group-choice">
  <legend>Check boxes <span class="mzp-c-fieldnote">Example with a fieldnote.</span></legend>
  <div class="mzp-c-input-choice">
    <input type="checkbox" name="checkboxes" id="checkbox-c2">
    <label for="checkbox-c2">Option 1</label>
  </div>
  <div class="mzp-c-input-choice">
    <input type="checkbox" name="checkboxes" id="checkbox-c3">
    <label for="checkbox-c3">Option 2</label>
  </div>
</fieldset>

